  "body": "<p>There were so many things I loved about <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/blue-note?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico's Blue Note kits</a>. The only thing I didn't love was not being able to carve out more time to create with these kits. I started a few bits and pieces and will be sure to include them in future layouts and Project Life spreads. I even went so far as taking a photo of my favorite things with intentions of Instagramming it on reveal day, but alas forgot. Blaming mommy brain once again.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/cfc203cd37ba97dd.jpg?v=1782537940\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>This month I got the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/blue-note-scrapbook-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Scrapbook kit</a> - love the Heidi Swapp alphas, <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/blue-note-project-life-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Project Life kit</a>, as well as <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/sinatra?aff=6cc2c70f\">Sinatra</a> and the Project Life add-on, Armstrong, which is already sold out. And here is what I created:</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/dde890274871b0cc.jpg?v=1782537943\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/fa6eec0c95857d12.jpg?v=1782537946\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ba7a325b28c28610.jpg?v=1782537949\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>For this layout, I used the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/blue-note-scrapbook-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Scrapbook kit</a> only. I'll show you how it all came together in a couple days.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/3380b7c09d36cf7c.jpg?v=1782537951\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>And here is some VERY exciting news!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/2df1ca63c9bf236c.jpg?v=1782537954\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Small Business Saturday means big savings for Studio Calico <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/classrooms?aff=6cc2c70f\">class</a> enthusiasts!  We're bringing back seven of our most popular <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/classrooms?aff=6cc2c70f\">classes</a> and are offering them to you at an all time low price.  Your favorite industry experts sharing their best tips and tricks at up to 70% off the original price!</p><p>For a limited time, my class that ran only for a month back in February 2012, <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/classrooms/stretch-your-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Stretch Your Kit</a> is available for just $12. I highlight tons of tips for making the most of your kits - there's PDF's along with videos and projects from contributors. You can also get the bundle at a huge discount by adding all of the classes to your cart and using the code: SBSCLASS.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/102c350bb3a3d07c.jpg?v=1782537957\"/>\n\n\n</figure>"
